## Usage

### Installation

Install latest from the GitHub
[repository](https://github.com/sky1ove/af_kit):

``` sh
$ pip install git+https://github.com/sky1ove/af_kit.git
```

or from [pypi](https://pypi.org/project/af_kit/)

``` sh
$ pip install af_kit
```
